<view class="page login-page"><view class="login-hero"><view class="brand-mark"><image class="brand-icon" src="{{a}}" mode="aspectFit"/></view><view class="login-title">承运商登录</view><view class="login-subtitle">接收订单、维护线路、处理履约节点</view></view><view class="login-form"><view class="field"><text class="label">手机号码</text><view class="input-wrapper"><text class="phone-prefix">+86</text><input class="input phone-input" type="number" maxlength="11" placeholder="请输入您的手机号" placeholder-class="placeholder-style" value="{{b}}" bindinput="{{c}}"/></view></view><view class="field"><text class="label">验证码</text><view class="input-wrapper code-wrapper"><input class="input code-input" type="number" maxlength="6" placeholder="请输入 6 位验证码" placeholder-class="placeholder-style" value="{{d}}" bindinput="{{e}}"/><button class="code-btn" disabled="{{g}}" bindtap="{{h}}">{{f}}</button></view><view class="code-tip">验证码 10 分钟内有效，请注意查收短信</view></view><button class="primary-btn login-btn" loading="{{i}}" bindtap="{{j}}">登录 / 注册</button><view class="agreement-wrapper"><label class="agreement-checkbox" bindtap="{{o}}"><checkbox checked="{{k}}" color="#1677ff" style="transform:scale(0.7)" catchtap="{{l}}"/><text class="agreement-text"> 我已阅读并同意 <text class="agreement-link" catchtap="{{m}}">《注册协议》</text>与 <text class="agreement-link" catchtap="{{n}}">《隐私协议》</text></text></label></view></view><view class="login-footnote">新手机号验证后自动创建承运商账号</view></view>